Third Department,

May, 1945.

(May 9, 1945.) In the Matter of the Claim of Hazel Sheppard, Respondent, against Albert J. Demps et al., Appellants. State Industrial Board, Respondent.

Motioa *791to amend notice of appeal from a decision of the Industrial Board. The appeal was taken to the Court of Appeals and dismissed by that court [266 App. Div. 45, appeal dismissed 291 N. Y. 773], No appeal is pending now in any court. Motion denied. All concur.
